== Asnubbc ==
Timttawin f tutlayt taɣdimst smunn-tn sin imsnilsn. Timttawin timzwura ifsr-tnt Adolphe de Calassanti Motylinski g 1903 d 1904. Gant twwuriwin n -{Jacques Lanfry}-, lli iɣama g ɣadamis zɣ 1944 ar 1945 ifsr snat twuriwin-nns nna istuhmman ɣ 1968 d 1973, asagʷm yufn amzwaru. Ur jjun sul tettuskar kra n usnubbc amaynu f udɣar-ad sɣ wakud-ann. Ɣ tgariwin-ad, ifsr [[:en:Maarten Kossmann|Kossmann]] (2013) yat tjṛṛumt tatrat ibiddn f tmttawin n -{Lanfry}-.

== Uṭṭun n imsiwln ==
Iqddr -{Lanfry}- is llan 4,000 n umsiwl iɣ kullu ggutn<ref>Lanfry (1973:iv).</ref>. Uṭṭun ɣ tidt ur ittussan min turda. Ar isawal -{Ethnologue}- f yan uṭṭan dar 10,000 ɣ 2006 d 2,000 yaḍn iddrn bṛṛa n udɣar. Maccan uṭṭun n 10,000 iga tamuttrt n imzdaɣn Ɣadamis lli kullu ur igin imsiwln n tutlayt taɣdimst. Nnig n aya, Uṭṭun ad n 2,000 n umzwag amswil ibdd f yan usagʷm bahra iqburn<ref>''Encyclopaedia of Islam'', 2nd edition, article ''Ghadāmis'' (1952): 2,000 persons with a background in Ghadames living in Tunis; quoted by Lanfry (1973:iv).</ref>. Ethnologue ar tt issiḍin am tutlayt illan g imizi n unɣubu "6b" (Threatened).

== Tutlayt ==
Taɣdimst tga [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tutlayt tamaziɣt]] s waḍu-nns, tari mnnawt tmẓlay tisnmslitin d tsnalɣanin timyiwnin. Amawal n tɣdimst, mk lli t izmmim Lafry, ar immal iḍiṣ idrusn zzɣ tɛṛabt. Ur ta illi kra n umsasa f ussinw n tɣdimst gr trabbut n tutlayin timaziɣin. -{Aikhenvald}- d -{Militarev}- (1984) ar tt ssiḍinn f [[Tutlayin timaziɣin tigmuḍanin|tmaziɣt n ugmuḍ]]. [[:en:Maarten Kossmann|-{Kossmann}-]] (1999) ar tt ismun d [[Tutlayt Tawilant|Twilant]]. [[:en:Ethnologue|-{Ethnologue}-]] ismma tt am [[Tajanat n ugmuḍ]] g ussinw-nns.

